	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_002067_0001"><!--pb/@n='78r'--></pb>
<lb/><p rend="center">Monday morning</p>
<lb/>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">My dear <persName>Waller</persName></p>
<lb/><p>Could you draw
<lb/>a gigantic human
<lb/>head - not an
<lb/>ugly one - with
<lb/>a lip ring in it
<lb/>to <choice><orig>shew</orig><reg>show</reg></choice> at the
<lb/>theatre tonight.
<lb/>I shall see you 
<lb/>at the section of 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_002067_0002"><!--pb/@n='78v'--></pb>
<lb/>of geography today</p>
<lb/><p><persName><choice><abbr>D L</abbr><expan>David Livingstone</expan></choice></persName> is in <add place="below">^</add> <add place="above">the</add> terrific
<lb/>labour pains of
<lb/>his <term type="animal">mouse</term> - <choice><sic>wont</sic><corr>won't</corr></choice>
<lb/>mention <persName>Bishop <choice><abbr>T.</abbr><expan>Tozer</expan></choice></persName>
<lb/>at all</p><!-- Bleedthrough from recto side evident HB 9/25/12 -->

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_002067_0003"><!--pb/@n='79r'--></pb><!-- No Livingstone text on this page -->

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_002067_0004"><!--pb/@n='79v'--></pb><!-- This page contains no text --><!-- Bleedthrough from recto side evident HB 9/25/12 -->
			
